page.title: 05Brownies
page.content: { Brownies}is on{Wednesday}at{6 o'clock to{half past seven.}You go when you are seven years old.Our leaders are{ {Brown owl,Tawney owl,Snowy owl}and{ {Little owl}.When we go we have to pay twenty-five pence for subscription.We have a book where we tick off our names.We do work for badges.At the moment we are doing a 'Safty in the home badge'.I am doing the 'Toy makers badge'.You have to do three things:at the moment I am making a scrapbook and I have already made a cuddly toy.Our {Siker}is{Anita.}I am the{Seconder.}We have sweets which we call tuck.We also play games.I am in the{Garden gnomes.} My friend is a{Lepricorn.Mrs Blud}is{ {Brown owl,Mrs Holmes}is{Tawney owl, {Karen}is{Snowy owl}and{Joanne Blud}is {Little owl. { { }
